{"tid":2367330,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"想試吓開班教designer寫code 做frontend development","createTime":"2021-01-15T09:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T08:19:43.000Z","uid":223799,"like":11,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"99c18d8fdf80eca6b572d53b56cbff1a1f45bc59","tid":2367330,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"我本身係non-cs，自學咗一年半html, css 同js之後，入行做frontend developer，以成爲專業嘅frontend developer 做目標，職位上而家跳到去intermediate level。<br />\n<br />\n因爲呢排得閒，自己又有地方，所以想試吓開班，用non-CS，容易入口嘅方法教designer 做frontend development 要用到嘅技術，內容包括html, css, javascript同 svg。以我轉工跳槽嘅經驗，如果ux/ui designer學咗下面嘅嘢，應該可以加6~10k。<br />\n<br />\n暫時我得閒教嘅時間應該會係星期六、日嘅夜晚，如果有興趣嘅，可以用tg搵我：<a href=\"https://t.me/fargohighfly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffargohighfly&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=bc0412db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fargohighfly</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我嘅github repo，有我寫嘅open source project做參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/winston0410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fwinston0410&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=2b197290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/winston0410</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係frontend developer嘅roadmap， 我會以佢做參考慢慢由淺入深教落去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://roadmap.sh/frontend\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Froadmap.sh%2Ffrontend&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=6b83de56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://roadmap.sh/frontend</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時我諗住教嘅內容會有呢啲：<br />\n<br />\n**HTML**<br />\n- Semantic HTML<br />\n<br />\n**CSS**<br />\n- Box model<br />\n- Relative and absolute positioning<br />\n- Flexbox<br />\n- Grid<br />\n<br />\n**CSS(Advance)**<br />\n- CSS pre-processing<br />\n- Atomic CSS<br />\n- Mixin and Variable<br />\n<br />\n**Javascript**<br />\n- Basic syntax<br />\n- Use of browser APIs<br />\n<br />\n**Javascript(Advance)**<br />\n- Functional Programming<br />\n- Promise and Async<br />\n- Event loops, macro and micro tasks<br />\n- Factory functions<br />\n- CJS vs ESM<br />\n- Use of Babel and AST Transformation<br />\n<br />\n**SVG**<br />\n- viewBox<br />\n- Reuse components with <code>&lt;g&gt;</code> , <code>&lt;use&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code><br />\n- animation (SMIL)<br />\n- Control SVG with Javascript"},{"pid":"d2dae56cc070366de5fe22691895dd11f7da237f","tid":2367330,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0838885033d05b47a917bb884d856ceab9b71872","tid":2367330,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"學左一年js 近排玩緊react 想遲d 轉行做frond end<br />\n支持支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9f10650f3aa0eb6315043825e758608622f340","tid":2367330,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"non-cs 點樣入到行"},{"pid":"36ee44eb83145e083db33cb1d3aa809684c1fd12","tid":2367330,"uid":36014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"幾錢？"},{"pid":"0777fa0d3f2d57f63ac2b260dfa609e358aab88a","tid":2367330,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"0b9f10650f3aa0eb6315043825e758608622f340","tid":2367330,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"non-cs 點樣入到行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"自學 之後showcase project 畀人睇"},{"pid":"ff215beaba2d8442451f778309abee4c8ec6cb0d","tid":2367330,"uid":383818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"有興趣，可以點參加，幾多錢<span class=\"small\"></span>"},{"pid":"09c1d4be630308bea30fdf7968fc7123f7c31705","tid":2367330,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"36ee44eb83145e083db33cb1d3aa809684c